File system browser

Manages Extension -> Mimetype database.
Create RUN shortcuts for file:// directories
Create VIEW shortcuts file:// based on mimetype

Handles Intents { action:RUN mimeType:text/directory }



Options Menu
------------
  [Copy]
  [Move]
  [Delete]
  New Directory
  Preferences
  -----------
    Hide Dot Files      On
    Back Changes ..     False
    Allow / access      False
    Font Size           Small
    Home Directory      /sdcard
    Mime Types
    ----------
      txt               text/*
      html              text/html
      png,gif,jpg,bmp   image/*
      mpg,wmv,mov,avi   video/*
      wav,mp3,wma       audio/*
  Help


Context Menu
------------
  Open as
  Yank
  Rename
